metadata.name: The Grand Kohantuar
metadata.description:
Often times Mortal chooses the path which is forbidden and prohibited by many.

This time - To grasp fruitful victory he seeked foul fellow..
The Grand Master Kohantuar.

Kohantuar was mischievous head of known cult Majauira - after the defeat from King Brajirell, he took shelter in forest of Gahaf√§hr.

For centuries, he rotten in darkness of doom and accepted fate of the unbreakable curse.

But life chose the different plans and sent a mortal to wake the beast and to offer him a journey with him in battle with King Brajirell.
